# ğŸ—³ï¸ Online Voting App

A secure and efficient online voting platform built with **Node.js**, **Express**, **MongoDB**, and **EJS**.  
This project allows users to register, log in, and cast votes securely, while admins can manage candidates and monitor live results.

---

## ğŸš€ Features
- User Signup & Login (with express-session)
- Role-based Access (Admin & Voter)
- Add, Update, Delete Candidates (Admin only)
- Secure Voting System (One vote per user)
- Password Encryption using Bcrypt
- RESTful API routes
- EJS frontend with dynamic views

---

## ğŸ§° Tech Stack
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js  
- **Frontend:** EJS, HTML, CSS  
- **Database:** MongoDB  
- **Authentication:** express-session  
- **Deployment:** Render / Railway  

